<b>Alma:</b> (I have no idea how to revive the dead!)
<b>Narration:</b> I absolutely can't help him.
<b>Narration:</b> As much as I've read up on the subject, I still know little more than what I did before I started--so next to nothing.
<b>Narration:</b> Decidedly, I may wind up doing more harm than good.
<b>Narration:</b> ...
<b>Narration:</b> The look of desparation on his face thrusts itself to the forefront of my mind, despite my decision.
<b>Narration:</b> His brown eyes, bright and pleading, looking right at me. 
<b>Narration:</b> ...
<b>Narration:</b> Is this the right choice...?

